WEBVTT

00:00:10.093 --> 00:00:15.974
In this world like nuts packed in a bag,

00:00:15.974 --> 00:00:22.856
Everyone is snuggling up
to someone they meet

00:00:22.856 --> 00:00:28.987
We are mixed in there and smiling

00:00:28.987 --> 00:00:34.659
By pretending we are
all nuts like peanuts

00:00:34.659 --> 00:00:37.579
On the template of happiness,

00:00:37.579 --> 00:00:41.124
Behind the surface
which is literally picturesque

00:00:41.124 --> 00:00:45.336
We can't be as we are,

00:00:45.336 --> 00:00:50.675
Even when we put our hands
together sitting around a table

00:00:50.675 --> 00:00:57.766
Home with full of secrets
and patches, you know?

00:00:57.766 --> 00:01:00.810
Even though I chew up
the real emotions,

00:01:00.810 --> 00:01:03.980
they still don't disappear

00:01:03.980 --> 00:01:05.565
They are still stuck in my teeth

00:01:05.565 --> 00:01:08.568
My life is so insecure and drifting,

00:01:08.568 --> 00:01:10.779
And I know

00:01:10.779 --> 00:01:14.199
Every day is so mediocre,

00:01:14.199 --> 00:01:18.995
but I'm here and so are you

00:01:18.995 --> 00:01:25.376
Just by this truth,
my stomach feels heavy

00:01:32.008 --> 00:01:34.469
(Eden Academy's Designated Uniform Retailers)

00:01:39.015 --> 00:01:42.268
99.5 cm...

00:01:42.268 --> 00:01:44.979
Anya's got 2 mm taller than before!

00:01:44.979 --> 00:01:46.397
Probably just an error, right?

00:01:46.397 --> 00:01:47.857
Who can tell?

00:01:47.857 --> 00:01:50.485
Children are so quick
in growing up, after all.

00:01:50.485 --> 00:01:51.528
Right they are.

00:01:51.528 --> 00:01:55.198
Then I guess we'll just make it
a bit bigger in case she grows taller.

00:01:55.573 --> 00:01:59.786
But still... I can't believe
you're married already, Yor.

00:01:59.786 --> 00:02:04.165
You could've told me when
you visited us the other day, though!

00:02:04.165 --> 00:02:06.960
I'm sorry... for not letting
you know back then.

00:02:06.960 --> 00:02:11.506
And your daughter's going
to the prestigious Eden, too!

00:02:11.506 --> 00:02:12.966
Congrats.

00:02:12.966 --> 00:02:15.051
Thank very much.

00:02:15.051 --> 00:02:18.096
Are you an Eden alumnus too, Sir?

00:02:18.096 --> 00:02:18.888
No.

00:02:18.888 --> 00:02:21.141
I went to a third-rate school
in the countryside...

00:02:21.141 --> 00:02:23.768
Oh, you should be careful, then.

00:02:23.768 --> 00:02:25.478
Eden really upholds traditional values,

00:02:25.478 --> 00:02:29.065
and I heard there are barriers between
alumni and non-alumni parents,

00:02:29.065 --> 00:02:32.986
and that gives birth to discrimination
and bullying among the children.

00:02:33.486 --> 00:02:35.947
There's also the case of violence
by scholarship students,

00:02:35.947 --> 00:02:38.825
and the discord between boarding
students and commuting students...

00:02:38.825 --> 00:02:43.830
Huh... Looks like commuting students are
frequently kidnapped these days, too.

00:02:43.830 --> 00:02:47.750
Only the rich are able
to go to Eden, after all.

00:02:47.750 --> 00:02:50.336
Anya won't be going to school.

00:02:50.336 --> 00:02:51.296
Huh?!

00:02:51.671 --> 00:02:53.089
Oh, I'm sorry.

00:02:53.089 --> 00:02:55.550
I didn't mean to scare you.

00:02:55.550 --> 00:02:58.678
There are also lots of
fun things there, so it's okay!

00:02:58.678 --> 00:03:00.388
Okay, we're done here.

00:03:01.389 --> 00:03:04.184
So... your orders are a uniform set,

00:03:04.184 --> 00:03:07.979
a winter coat, and a sweater vest.
That makes it three, then.

00:03:07.979 --> 00:03:11.399
Since you're a regular customer,
we'll have them ready fast.

00:03:11.399 --> 00:03:15.695
Oh, you can find other required items
in the shop in the corner of the street.

00:03:15.695 --> 00:03:17.739
That's a lot of money.

00:03:21.701 --> 00:03:23.536
Hm? What's wrong?

00:03:23.536 --> 00:03:25.580
I'm scared of kidnappers.

00:03:25.580 --> 00:03:26.581
Oh, really?

00:03:26.581 --> 00:03:28.082
Getting to it already, aren't you?

00:03:28.791 --> 00:03:31.753
Do you mind if we eat outside today, Yor?

00:03:31.753 --> 00:03:33.546
Sure!

00:03:33.546 --> 00:03:36.841
No kidnapper in restaurant?

00:03:37.383 --> 00:03:38.843
Here's our recommendation for today:

00:03:38.843 --> 00:03:42.513
Pork sauté with powpaw sauce and porcini,

00:03:42.513 --> 00:03:45.475
and potato potage.

00:03:45.475 --> 00:03:46.476
Po?

00:03:46.476 --> 00:03:47.435
Looks delicious.

00:03:47.435 --> 00:03:48.603
Code P, huh.

00:03:49.395 --> 00:03:51.272
A call for briefing, I see.

00:03:51.272 --> 00:03:55.568
Five days from now at
13:00 in Safe House D.

00:03:55.568 --> 00:03:57.195
Roger that.

00:03:57.195 --> 00:04:00.740
But they really need to
stop contacting me like this.

00:04:00.740 --> 00:04:02.492
It's kind of bugging me.

00:04:02.533 --> 00:04:05.495
(5 Days Later)

00:04:05.495 --> 00:04:06.579
Yes.

00:04:06.579 --> 00:04:08.081
Oh, hello.

00:04:08.081 --> 00:04:10.500
Oh, they're done already?

00:04:10.500 --> 00:04:11.584
All right.

00:04:11.584 --> 00:04:13.002
We'll come by to pick them up today.

00:04:13.586 --> 00:04:14.504
See you, then.

00:04:17.590 --> 00:04:19.008
My uniform's done?!

00:04:19.008 --> 00:04:20.760
Looks like it.

00:04:21.594 --> 00:04:23.763
However, today's the day for briefing.

00:04:24.389 --> 00:04:25.765
Sorry to trouble you, Yor,

00:04:25.765 --> 00:04:28.101
but could you take Anya
with you there as well?

00:04:28.101 --> 00:04:30.520
I've got work to do.

00:04:31.479 --> 00:04:32.563
Of course.

00:04:32.563 --> 00:04:34.065
Leave it to me.

00:04:34.065 --> 00:04:37.068
I might be coming home late,

00:04:37.068 --> 00:04:39.779
so feel free to order
something for dinner tonight.

00:04:39.779 --> 00:04:40.655
Okay.

00:04:40.655 --> 00:04:42.532
Safe trip.

