(Nickname: Handler)

00:05:20.778 --> 00:05:22.071
Hello, Handler.

00:05:22.071 --> 00:05:23.323
What's the business?

00:05:23.781 --> 00:05:26.326
Before that...

00:05:26.326 --> 00:05:28.578
What's up with the high
expense the other day?!

00:05:28.578 --> 00:05:31.289
Castle and royal furniture rental fees?!

00:05:31.289 --> 00:05:33.207
You trying to screw
with our wise budget?!

00:05:33.207 --> 00:05:35.293
And here are some additional invoices.

00:05:35.293 --> 00:05:37.211
School admission is
a lot of work, I suppose.

00:05:37.211 --> 00:05:39.964
I commend your bravery for
handing those nonchalantly.

00:05:39.964 --> 00:05:42.133
These and those are
necessary expenses.

00:05:42.133 --> 00:05:43.593
Fine, then.

00:05:43.593 --> 00:05:44.218
So...

00:05:44.886 --> 00:05:48.848
We'd like to confirm the execution for
Phase 2 of Operation Strix with you.

00:05:48.848 --> 00:05:51.726
Though, I don't think a wise
agent like you would need this.

00:05:51.726 --> 00:05:53.102
Well...

00:05:53.102 --> 00:05:55.938
I've been leaving things
to chance lately, so...

00:05:56.481 --> 00:05:58.775
Phase 2: The Social Gathering.

00:05:58.775 --> 00:06:02.445
For the purpose of this briefing,
we'll review the system in Eden.

00:06:02.987 --> 00:06:04.572
Eden College.

00:06:04.572 --> 00:06:06.991
Around 2,500 students are
admitted to this school.

00:06:06.991 --> 00:06:10.453
With a total of 13 grades
from 6 to 19 years of age.

00:06:10.453 --> 00:06:12.580
Scholarship, sports, and arts.

00:06:12.580 --> 00:06:15.958
It's a top-class educational
institution excelling in various fields.

00:06:15.958 --> 00:06:19.379
And the best and most talented students
are hand-picked in that elite school.

00:06:19.379 --> 00:06:23.007
They are the scholarship students,
dubbed the Imperial Scholars.

00:06:23.007 --> 00:06:26.010
In order for you to attend
Desmond's social gathering,

00:06:26.010 --> 00:06:30.348
your daughter must be part
of this Imperial Scholars.

00:06:30.348 --> 00:06:32.475
And in order for your daughter
to become a scholarship student,

00:06:32.475 --> 00:06:36.479
she must gather eight medals
of merit, dubbed the Stella Stars.

00:06:36.479 --> 00:06:37.939
The medals are awarded

00:06:37.939 --> 00:06:40.608
for outstanding academic performance
and contribution to society.

00:06:41.067 --> 00:06:42.360
In other words,

00:06:42.360 --> 00:06:45.780
you must first raise your daughter
until she becomes an honour student.

00:06:45.780 --> 00:06:49.617
Feel free to use any means
necessary to achieve this.

00:06:49.617 --> 00:06:51.285
And in contrast,

00:06:51.285 --> 00:06:53.579
your daughter will be
awarded the Tonitrus Bolts

00:06:53.579 --> 00:06:56.374
for poor academic
performances and misconducts.

00:06:56.374 --> 00:07:00.253
Gather eight of these, and it's
instant expulsion for her, so be careful.

00:07:01.879 --> 00:07:02.880
- Now for the detailed plan discussion...

00:07:02.880 --> 00:07:05.007
