00:07:22.650 --> 00:07:24.068
Does Anya look cute?

00:07:24.068 --> 00:07:26.612
So cute, so cute!

00:07:26.612 --> 00:07:28.406
Just go home already, will you?

00:07:28.406 --> 00:07:29.407
