00:07:30.074 --> 00:07:32.493
Anya wants to go for a wok with this!

00:07:32.493 --> 00:07:33.786
Let's do it, then!

00:07:35.788 --> 00:07:37.582
Come again!

00:07:37.582 --> 00:07:41.377
La-la-la-la-la~

00:07:41.377 --> 00:07:43.588
Should we visit the park as well?

00:07:45.381 --> 00:07:46.883
It's Anya in a uniform!

00:07:46.883 --> 00:07:47.508
Baa!

00:07:47.508 --> 00:07:49.177
It's Anya in a uniform!

00:07:49.177 --> 00:07:49.886
Baa!

00:07:51.596 --> 00:07:53.347
What a cute daughter you have.

00:07:54.348 --> 00:07:56.100
She's going to Eden?

00:07:56.100 --> 00:07:58.186
Wow, I'm so jealous...

00:07:58.186 --> 00:08:00.271
Oh... hello.

00:08:00.271 --> 00:08:03.065
Mom, I'm hungry.

00:08:03.065 --> 00:08:05.067
What do you want for lunch?

00:08:05.067 --> 00:08:07.069
Salisbury steak!

00:08:10.323 --> 00:08:12.658
So you prefer your old mama, huh!

00:08:12.658 --> 00:08:15.077
I want to be with them forever!

00:08:17.163 --> 00:08:20.791
I know that we're just a fake family...

00:08:20.791 --> 00:08:21.584
But...

00:08:22.376 --> 00:08:24.378
I wonder if I...

00:08:24.378 --> 00:08:27.381
...could act like a proper mother for her?

00:08:28.591 --> 00:08:30.885
Mother!

00:08:31.260 --> 00:08:34.597
Anya has shown Anya's
cuteness to everyone!

00:08:34.597 --> 00:08:37.892
Come on, you can't dirty your
uniform before the entrance ceremony.

00:08:38.392 --> 00:08:39.769
Say, Anya.

00:08:39.769 --> 00:08:42.271
Why don't we drop by the supermarket?

00:08:42.271 --> 00:08:43.147
Hm?

00:08:43.147 --> 00:08:45.900
Loid said he'll be
coming home late tonight,

00:08:45.900 --> 00:08:47.985
so I'll make you dinner!

00:08:47.985 --> 00:08:48.819
Oh!

00:08:48.819 --> 00:08:50.404
Can you?

00:08:50.404 --> 00:08:52.698
Yes! I'll do my best!

00:08:53.991 --> 00:08:56.369
Hey, is that Eden's uniform?

00:08:56.369 --> 00:08:56.953
Hm?

00:08:58.287 --> 00:08:59.997
So the woman next to her is the mom?

00:08:59.997 --> 00:09:01.457
Must be a maid, right?

00:09:01.457 --> 00:09:04.794
What kind of rich guys
would go shopping by themselves?

00:09:04.794 --> 00:09:08.089
Oh, I could use some allowances now.

00:09:08.089 --> 00:09:09.465
Me too.

00:09:10.591 --> 00:09:14.971
Well, as long as there's meat
and vegetables, I should be good, right?

00:09:15.388 --> 00:09:17.557
I can't tell which one and
what kind I should buy,

00:09:17.557 --> 00:09:19.600
so I'll just buy every one of them.

00:09:19.600 --> 00:09:20.518
Baa!

00:09:22.270 --> 00:09:24.313
Anya will wait outside,
it's boring here!

00:09:24.313 --> 00:09:25.940
Don't go too far away, okay!

00:09:30.778 --> 00:09:32.947
Good day, Princess.

00:09:32.947 --> 00:09:35.491
Be a good girl for us, okay?

00:09:35.491 --> 00:09:39.287
We'll let you go once we've
got allowances from your maid.

00:09:39.287 --> 00:09:40.496
Bad guys...!

00:09:41.080 --> 00:09:44.000
Bullying and kidnapping
tend to happen at Eden...

00:09:44.458 --> 00:09:46.460
It's real...!

00:09:49.213 --> 00:09:51.924
I heard this uniform sells for a lot.

00:09:51.924 --> 00:09:53.175
Oh, that's nice.

00:09:53.175 --> 00:09:54.844
Now, Miss. If you could take off—

00:09:59.890 --> 00:10:02.602
What are you doing...?

00:10:02.602 --> 00:10:04.395
Oh, boy!

00:10:04.395 --> 00:10:06.981
You gotta pay extra for the hospital now!

00:10:06.981 --> 00:10:09.066
Give me your wallet, maid.

00:10:09.066 --> 00:10:12.778
I've used all the money in my
wallet, so there's none left.

00:10:12.778 --> 00:10:14.947
So please, take it.

00:10:15.281 --> 00:10:16.449
Oh, really?

00:10:16.449 --> 00:10:19.285
Then we'll just strip this girl
down and be done with her.

00:10:19.285 --> 00:10:22.455
You'll be losing your job anyway,

00:10:22.455 --> 00:10:25.625
so just go back to the
countryside, you shitty maid!

00:10:28.919 --> 00:10:31.380
W-With bare hands...?!

00:10:33.758 --> 00:10:36.218
I am her mother!

00:10:36.218 --> 00:10:38.763
If you don't want to end
up like those vegetables,

00:10:38.763 --> 00:10:40.514
get out of here right now!

00:10:42.683 --> 00:10:44.185
Mother...

00:10:45.561 --> 00:10:47.396
Are you okay?

00:10:47.396 --> 00:10:50.900
I'm sorry. It's all because
I took my eyes off you...

00:10:50.900 --> 00:10:52.151
There, there...

00:10:52.568 --> 00:10:55.363
I've messed up our groceries, too...

00:10:55.363 --> 00:10:57.740
I'm really a bad mother...

00:11:02.995 --> 00:11:06.290
Anya loves a strong and cool mother!

00:11:06.290 --> 00:11:07.625
There, there.

00:11:08.292 --> 00:11:10.628
Finisher punch! Bam!

00:11:10.628 --> 00:11:12.797
Y-You're embarrassing me...

00:11:12.797 --> 00:11:13.964
Mother!

00:11:14.465 --> 00:11:16.092
Train Anya how to do it!

00:11:16.092 --> 00:11:17.343
T-Train?

00:11:18.678 --> 00:11:22.098
I know it's dangerous
to be Eden's student.

00:11:22.098 --> 00:11:26.560
But if I train and become
stronger, it won't be scary!

00:11:26.560 --> 00:11:29.355
I can do my best at school
without having to die!

00:11:29.689 --> 00:11:31.982
I want to be like you!

00:11:33.275 --> 00:11:37.488
Though I can't act like a normal mother...

00:11:37.488 --> 00:11:40.991
I'll just have to do
my best at what I can!

00:11:40.991 --> 00:11:41.867
All right.

00:11:41.867 --> 00:11:44.078
Let's go home and train now.

00:11:44.078 --> 00:11:44.995
Training!

00:11:49.083 --> 00:11:50.626
