00:11:50.876 --> 00:11:51.669
Hah!

00:11:52.086 --> 00:11:52.878
Hah!

00:11:52.878 --> 00:11:53.713
Hm?

00:11:53.713 --> 00:11:55.297
What are you two doing?

00:11:55.297 --> 00:11:56.799
Preparing for school!

00:11:56.799 --> 00:11:57.717
Hah!

00:11:58.384 --> 00:11:59.176
Hah!

00:11:59.468 --> 00:12:00.177
Hah!

