You all are the chosen ones.

00:12:08.894 --> 00:12:10.396
Through your own efforts,

00:12:10.396 --> 00:12:13.482
and those of your parents,
you have successfully passed...

00:12:13.482 --> 00:12:16.694
...through the narrow gates
of our Eden Academy.

00:12:16.694 --> 00:12:21.866
To our glorious 228
new members of our school,

00:12:22.491 --> 00:12:24.285
I congratulate you on joining us!

00:12:24.285 --> 00:12:27.788
The whole Eden Academy
community warmly welcomes you all.

00:12:28.664 --> 00:12:31.000
I've finally made it this far.

00:12:31.000 --> 00:12:34.170
Father, there's a lot of people
wearing the same clothes as Anya!

00:12:34.170 --> 00:12:36.505
Yes. That's what you call a uniform.

00:12:36.505 --> 00:12:39.884
I still have mountains of problems, but...

00:12:39.884 --> 00:12:41.385
Look, Twilight.

00:12:41.385 --> 00:12:44.889
There's a condition if you want to
participate in Desmond's social gathering.

00:12:44.889 --> 00:12:48.267
That is, your daughter must be
selected as one of the Imperial Scholars.

00:12:48.267 --> 00:12:51.687
To do this, she will have to
be first in various subjects.

00:12:51.687 --> 00:12:57.818
Remember, the future of the East
and West depends on this operation.

00:12:58.194 --> 00:12:59.987
Making this girl an elite student...

00:13:00.780 --> 00:13:02.573
I'm halfway through giving up on that.

00:13:02.573 --> 00:13:03.824
Shock!

00:13:03.824 --> 00:13:06.994
It's a bit of a stretch for her to always
be the best in this school,

00:13:06.994 --> 00:13:09.789
