He followed in his brother's
footsteps and got into Eden.

00:14:01.298 --> 00:14:04.176
I've already marked his name
when I found it on the candidate list.

00:14:04.176 --> 00:14:05.594
Jesse Capel.

00:14:05.594 --> 00:14:10.599
He's my Plan B in case of trouble on
making Anya an Imperial Scholar member.

00:14:10.599 --> 00:14:12.560
I call it "Operation Buddy-Buddy"!

00:14:12.560 --> 00:14:13.811
(Mission: 6 - Operation Buddy-Buddy)

00:14:13.811 --> 00:14:15.896
1. Be in the same class as him
(Mission: 6 - Operation Buddy-Buddy)

00:14:15.896 --> 00:14:17.481
and become buddy-buddy-like with him.

00:14:17.481 --> 00:14:18.566
2. Get invited by him

00:14:18.566 --> 00:14:20.693
(Come on in!)
along with her parent, that is me.

00:14:20.693 --> 00:14:21.235
3. Come into direct contact with my target.

00:14:21.235 --> 00:14:23.737
(Welcome!) (Hello!)
3. Come into direct contact with the target.

00:14:24.196 --> 00:14:26.782
Though I don't think it'll go so smoothly,

00:14:26.782 --> 00:14:28.284
but it's always good to have insurance.

00:14:28.284 --> 00:14:29.410
Anya Forger.

00:14:30.452 --> 00:14:31.662
Go on now.

00:14:33.581 --> 00:14:35.207
Back in the orphanage,

00:14:35.207 --> 00:14:38.252
Anya had lived together with
so many children of her age.

00:14:38.669 --> 00:14:41.505
I'll just believe
in her communication skills.

00:14:42.381 --> 00:14:44.758
The child of the evil boss...

00:14:45.384 --> 00:14:47.386
What's up with her...?

00:14:47.386 --> 00:14:48.762
Oh, don't tell me...

00:14:49.305 --> 00:14:52.308
She's fallen for my
handsomeness at first sight already?

00:14:52.308 --> 00:14:54.727
She's got a keen eye, huh?

00:14:56.228 --> 00:14:57.771
What a shy girl...

00:14:57.771 --> 00:14:59.189
That's cute.

00:14:59.189 --> 00:15:00.983
Becky Blackbell.

00:15:00.983 --> 00:15:01.692
Sigh...

00:15:02.610 --> 00:15:03.986
Nice to meet you!

00:15:05.195 --> 00:15:06.947
Hm? That kid...

00:15:07.489 --> 00:15:10.576
She's the daughter of the CEO of
a major military company, Blackbell!

00:15:11.285 --> 00:15:13.871
Behind her is the daughter of
the vice chairman of the Parliament!

00:15:13.871 --> 00:15:16.790
And there's the son of a VIP in the
Security Service among the boys too!

00:15:16.790 --> 00:15:20.169
Her classmates are a gold mine of Intel!

00:15:20.169 --> 00:15:23.088
You gotta get along with them, Anya!

00:15:23.088 --> 00:15:26.133
He's so hell-bent when it
comes to his daughter, I see.

00:15:26.133 --> 00:15:27.593
I'm Becky.

00:15:27.593 --> 00:15:28.886
What's your name?

00:15:28.886 --> 00:15:30.054
She looks so childish.

00:15:30.054 --> 00:15:32.806
I could at least be
her caretaker, I guess.

00:15:34.266 --> 00:15:34.975
Huh?!

00:15:34.975 --> 00:15:36.518
Hey!

00:15:36.518 --> 00:15:40.022
The homeroom teacher
will be Mr. Henderson.

00:15:40.773 --> 00:15:42.691
Oh, the nice teacher!

00:15:42.691 --> 00:15:44.777
So he wasn't fired, after all.

00:15:44.777 --> 00:15:47.196
It seems unfair that a housemaster
is demoted to a homeroom teacher...

00:15:47.196 --> 00:15:48.572
...for the grade students,

00:15:48.572 --> 00:15:51.283
but I guess he's lucky enough
to have this as a punishment.

00:15:51.283 --> 00:15:54.745
Hm... I'll go back to the basics
and properly educate them.

00:15:54.745 --> 00:15:55.871
Ah...

00:15:55.871 --> 00:15:59.166
Now, please follow your homeroom teachers...

00:15:59.166 --> 00:16:02.586
...as they give you a tour on the school,
and head to your respective classroom.

00:16:02.586 --> 00:16:06.382
As for the parents,
please wait in Ward C's lounge...

00:16:06.382 --> 00:16:09.301
...and have a pleasant chat with each other.

00:16:09.301 --> 00:16:10.803
I'm counting on you, Anya.

00:16:10.803 --> 00:16:13.764
You have to figure things out
on your own from now.

00:16:15.182 --> 00:16:16.892
Okey-dokey!

00:16:16.892 --> 00:16:18.727
You there! Stay in line!

00:16:18.727 --> 00:16:19.895
Huh!

00:16:19.895 --> 00:16:22.231
Oh, this is so worrying...

00:16:22.231 --> 00:16:24.608
Seeing your daughter off
really makes you anxious, right?

00:16:24.608 --> 00:16:25.776
I feel you.

00:16:27.277 --> 00:16:28.779
This is the cafeteria.

00:16:28.779 --> 00:16:32.908
Our first-class chefs serve
elegant food here every day.

00:16:33.367 --> 00:16:34.785
And beyond those doors...

00:16:34.785 --> 00:16:38.539
...is another cafeteria exclusive
to the Imperial Scholars.

00:16:38.872 --> 00:16:40.874
Anyone can become a Scholar,

00:16:40.874 --> 00:16:44.586
as long as you do elegantly in class,
and receive eight Stella Stars.

00:16:44.586 --> 00:16:47.089
You will do your best to be diligent now.

00:16:47.089 --> 00:16:48.132
Yes, Sir!

00:16:48.132 --> 00:16:50.259
In contrast, there are also punishments...

00:16:50.259 --> 00:16:53.429
and expulsions depending on the
amount of Tonitrus Bolts you have,

00:16:53.429 --> 00:16:54.471
so bear that in mind.

00:16:54.471 --> 00:16:56.390
Why is he looking at me?

00:16:56.390 --> 00:16:59.560
I bet you'll be a Scholar
in no time, Master Damian!

00:16:59.560 --> 00:17:00.894
Obviously.

00:17:00.894 --> 00:17:02.479
Of course!

00:17:02.479 --> 00:17:05.566
I'm the son of the chairman of
the National Unity Party, you see.

00:17:05.566 --> 00:17:06.775
- Huh?! Really?!
- Wow!

00:17:06.775 --> 00:17:09.987
My papa said that Desmond Group
has been a great help to our family!

00:17:09.987 --> 00:17:10.571
Hey!

00:17:10.571 --> 00:17:12.448
Enough with the chit-chat!

00:17:12.448 --> 00:17:13.782
That's just ridiculous.

00:17:16.910 --> 00:17:18.579
What about you?

00:17:18.579 --> 00:17:20.581
What does your dad do?

00:17:20.581 --> 00:17:23.917
Depending on the job level, I might
consider adding you to my friend list.

00:17:24.710 --> 00:17:27.296
I must endure it for the mission.

00:17:27.296 --> 00:17:29.673
A Sp— splendid heart doctor.

00:17:30.716 --> 00:17:32.801
So he's no big shot, huh.

00:17:32.801 --> 00:17:34.678
I bet you're not even that rich.

00:17:34.678 --> 00:17:35.679
Lame.

00:17:35.679 --> 00:17:37.890
Anya wants to go to your house to play.

00:17:37.890 --> 00:17:40.684
How dare you!
Know your place, pig!

00:17:40.684 --> 00:17:42.895
What a brazen commoner we have here.

00:17:42.895 --> 00:17:45.439
I'll catch your commoner germs, so get!

00:17:47.066 --> 00:17:49.985
All right, time to unleash the
finisher punch now!

00:17:49.985 --> 00:17:51.195
Look, Anya.

00:17:51.695 --> 00:17:52.488
Huh!

00:17:52.488 --> 00:17:55.199
Those who let their emotions
get the better of them...

00:17:55.199 --> 00:17:57.284
...and assert their strength
can't be considered truly strong.

00:17:57.284 --> 00:17:59.078
If you're just being teased,

00:17:59.078 --> 00:18:01.830
just put on a smile, and you'll do fine.
Like a cool big sister.

00:18:01.830 --> 00:18:03.457
Big sister...!

00:18:03.457 --> 00:18:07.669
Also, a smile a day keeps a fight away.

00:18:07.669 --> 00:18:09.171
You're so pathetic!

00:18:09.171 --> 00:18:11.298
At least say something back to them!

00:18:12.382 --> 00:18:14.468
Anya doesn't mind it a bit.

00:18:14.468 --> 00:18:15.594
Huh...?!

00:18:17.679 --> 00:18:19.098
Heh.

00:18:19.098 --> 00:18:22.976
Wh-What the heck's that
condescending smile for?!

00:18:22.976 --> 00:18:24.186
So much leeway!

00:18:24.186 --> 00:18:26.396
She's just like an adult! Amazing!

00:18:26.396 --> 00:18:28.732
I was mistaken to have
thought of her as childish!

00:18:28.732 --> 00:18:30.734
You're surprisingly mature enough, huh!

00:18:30.734 --> 00:18:32.236
I see you in a new light now!

00:18:32.236 --> 00:18:33.487
Mature...

00:18:38.117 --> 00:18:39.076
Heh...

00:18:40.744 --> 00:18:42.788
Don't get so carried away, you pig!

00:18:42.788 --> 00:18:44.581
You pig, pig, pig!

00:18:44.581 --> 00:18:47.376
Master Damian, please
do mind your vocabulary...

00:18:47.960 --> 00:18:48.794
What?

00:18:48.794 --> 00:18:50.546
Sure, she's as ugly as a pig
compared to me,

00:18:50.546 --> 00:18:52.214
but you don't have to go so far, do you?

00:18:52.214 --> 00:18:53.632
Shut up!

00:18:53.632 --> 00:18:56.009
You there! How many
times do I have to tell you?!

00:18:56.009 --> 00:18:58.137
You want a bolt already on your first day?!

00:18:58.470 --> 00:18:59.596
Damn!

00:18:59.596 --> 00:19:02.474
How dare you put me to shame...
You won't get away with this!

00:19:03.267 --> 00:19:04.685
You're a liar, Mother.

00:19:04.685 --> 00:19:06.562
The smile does nothing.

00:19:14.069 --> 00:19:14.486
Heh.

00:19:14.486 --> 00:19:17.656
Cut it out already, or I'll report you!

00:19:17.656 --> 00:19:20.075
You got proof that we did it?

00:19:20.075 --> 00:19:21.410
Right, right!

00:19:21.702 --> 00:19:23.162
Out of the way.

00:19:23.871 --> 00:19:25.914
Hey, smirking pig.

00:19:25.914 --> 00:19:29.668
I'm going to bully you to
my heart's content from now.

00:19:29.668 --> 00:19:33.255
And I'm also going to rip that smirk off
your face that you can't use it again.

00:19:33.255 --> 00:19:36.675
Even if she starts crying,
her heart doctor papa will cure him!

00:19:36.675 --> 00:19:39.761
Wow, now that's amazing!

00:19:39.761 --> 00:19:41.096
Good for you, eh!

00:19:44.266 --> 00:19:45.684
Hey, where are you looking?

00:19:45.684 --> 00:19:46.977
You scared?

00:19:58.655 --> 00:19:59.990
What's going on there?!

00:19:59.990 --> 00:20:03.076
Sir! This girl just hit Master Damian!

00:20:03.076 --> 00:20:03.785
Huh!

00:20:03.785 --> 00:20:06.538
I was just stretching out my hand
and he happened to be in front of me...

00:20:06.538 --> 00:20:07.497
Liar!

00:20:07.497 --> 00:20:09.541
Why are you trying to fool him?!

00:20:09.541 --> 00:20:12.794
Wait, you were actually checking if Mr.
Henderson was watching us earlier, right?!

00:20:12.794 --> 00:20:15.172
You got proof that I did it?

00:20:15.172 --> 00:20:18.508
Isn't this enough proof of
your big, heavy punch?!

00:20:19.092 --> 00:20:23.764
I would be ashamed of myself
if I testified perjury, Anya Forger.

00:20:25.474 --> 00:20:27.267
You've got it wrong, Sir!

00:20:27.267 --> 00:20:29.561
She's been holding back the whole time,

00:20:29.561 --> 00:20:30.687
but these guys...

00:20:31.647 --> 00:20:34.233
So it's true that you did hit him.

00:20:36.193 --> 00:20:37.819
Look, Anya.

00:20:37.819 --> 00:20:38.779
Huh!

00:20:38.779 --> 00:20:40.906
The right time to use force...

00:20:40.906 --> 00:20:45.244
...is, for example, when you have to help
your friend in a tight spot...

00:20:47.871 --> 00:20:50.499
H-He stepped...

00:20:51.166 --> 00:20:52.584
...on her foot earlier...

00:20:53.168 --> 00:20:55.504
So Anya got mad...

00:20:55.504 --> 00:20:57.214
I'm sorry...

00:20:58.757 --> 00:21:00.801
You did it for me?!

00:21:00.801 --> 00:21:02.177
Anya...

00:21:03.470 --> 00:21:05.389
- Thank you!
- While she contained her personal resentment,

00:21:05.389 --> 00:21:06.890
- she also has the spirit

00:21:06.890 --> 00:21:09.101
- I'm so touched!
- to stand firm against boys

00:21:09.101 --> 00:21:10.394
for the sake of her friend.

00:21:10.394 --> 00:21:13.772
Elegant indeed, Anya Forger.

00:21:13.772 --> 00:21:15.357
However...

00:21:16.275 --> 00:21:20.487
So Desmond and his wife
never showed up, huh.

00:21:20.487 --> 00:21:22.990
Well, there's no rush.

00:21:22.990 --> 00:21:24.574
As long as Anya's admitted here,

00:21:24.574 --> 00:21:26.076
- Attention, please!
- I have all the time I need.

00:21:26.076 --> 00:21:27.286
- The students have finished
- I've also developed

00:21:27.286 --> 00:21:28.787
- with their orientation,
- a reasonable network of contacts.

00:21:28.787 --> 00:21:30.497
so please gather at the courtyard.

00:21:30.497 --> 00:21:32.874
We'll be doing a group photo shoot there.

00:21:32.874 --> 00:21:34.459
Where's Anya?

00:21:34.459 --> 00:21:35.377
Forger.

00:21:36.211 --> 00:21:37.254
Come with me.

00:21:37.796 --> 00:21:39.881
She hit a boy...?

00:21:40.257 --> 00:21:41.466
Are you hurt?

00:21:41.466 --> 00:21:42.509
And it's Desmond's son,

00:21:42.509 --> 00:21:43.593
- out of all people...
- In a normal case,

00:21:43.593 --> 00:21:45.137
- What the heck happened...?
- an act of violence results in

00:21:45.137 --> 00:21:46.888
an instant three Tonitrus Bolts.

00:21:46.888 --> 00:21:49.891
But I used my discretion
and only gave her one.

00:21:49.891 --> 00:21:52.269
No further concessions can be made.

00:21:53.186 --> 00:21:54.980
I'm sorry, Loid!

00:21:54.980 --> 00:21:57.149
It's because I trained her
for the finisher punch...

00:21:57.149 --> 00:22:00.652
I'll inform the boy's parents as well.

00:22:00.652 --> 00:22:02.195
(Plan A - Plan B)
We've lost a point already

00:22:02.195 --> 00:22:03.864
(Plan A - Plan B)
on the first day of school...

00:22:03.864 --> 00:22:05.157
(Plan A - Plan B)
And Anya's relationship with Damian

00:22:05.157 --> 00:22:06.783
(Plan A - Plan B)
has plummeted, too...

00:22:08.785 --> 00:22:11.288
All right! I'm taking the picture now!

00:22:11.288 --> 00:22:15.000
You three on the far right!
Come on, smile more!

00:22:15.000 --> 00:22:16.084
Cheese!

00:22:25.635 --> 00:22:27.304
(Stella Stars Left for Scholarship: 8)

00:22:27.304 --> 00:22:28.805
(Tonitrus Bolts Left for Expulsion: 7)

00:22:28.805 --> 00:22:29.973
(Friendship Points with Damian: -100)

00:22:32.559 --> 00:22:34.019
Fighting with each other

00:22:34.019 --> 00:22:35.354
'Til almost everything was in ruins

00:22:35.354 --> 00:22:38.732
On this mischievous planet

00:22:38.732 --> 00:22:44.237
I've been an outsider
since the day I was born

00:22:44.237 --> 00:22:48.116
My tears have run dry

00:22:48.116 --> 00:22:54.414
The place I'm going back to is in my dreams

00:22:54.414 --> 00:22:55.749
I met you

00:22:55.749 --> 00:22:57.459
where I came spilling out

00:22:57.459 --> 00:23:00.462
You with all your secrets

00:23:00.462 --> 00:23:05.926
Pretending to be normal

00:23:05.926 --> 00:23:10.055
I'd given up searching
for a place where I belong

00:23:10.055 --> 00:23:17.604
Only to find out I had to
create one for myself all along

00:23:18.271 --> 00:23:20.273
We made a deal that day

00:23:20.857 --> 00:23:23.235
Thicker than blood

00:23:23.235 --> 00:23:28.365
A pact from heart to heart

00:23:28.365 --> 00:23:31.118
Shall we hold hands and head home?

00:23:31.118 --> 00:23:33.954
What should we eat tonight?

00:23:33.954 --> 00:23:36.665
"Here's what happened today"

00:23:36.665 --> 00:23:40.377
That's what I wanted to talk to you about

00:23:40.377 --> 00:23:42.129
Any and every day is

00:23:42.129 --> 00:23:44.714
A comedy with you

00:23:44.714 --> 00:23:47.551
Dancing on a creaking bed

00:23:47.551 --> 00:23:51.638
Rolling around in laughter

00:23:51.638 --> 00:23:58.437
We'll keep on with our
ridiculous everyday life

00:24:06.903 --> 00:24:09.865
(Mission: 7 - Target: The Second Son)
